The HTML structure of tasklists is as follows:  ul   class= task-list 
     li   class= task-list-item 
         input   type= checkbox   disabled=   checked= 
        item 1
     /li  /ul      Classes  Description      task-list  Attached to either the  ul  or  ol  tag and represents the entire list element.    task-list-item  This is attached the  li  tag and represents a an item in the list.     In order to style these we mainly remove the list type style and adjust the margins to align with normal list styles.  .markdown-body   .task-list-item   { 
   list-style-type :   none ;  }  .markdown-body   .task-list-item   input   { 
   margin :   0   4px   0.25em   -20px ; 
   vertical-align :   middle ;  }
